      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are a school data extraction assistant.\n\nFrom the search results below, extract all SCHOOLS only.\n\nReturn ONLY valid JSON array, no extra text, no markdown:\n\n[\n  {\n    \"school_name\": \"full school name here\",\n    \"district\": \"{{$json.district}}\",\n    \"website\": \"website url or empty string\",\n    \"offers_iit\": true,\n    \"offers_neet\": true\n  }\n]\n\nSTRICT RULES:\n- Only include actual schools\n- Do NOT include coaching centers\n- Do NOT include blogs or news\n- Do NOT include duplicates\n- If website unknown use empty string\n- Return empty array [] if nothing found\n- Return ONLY JSON, no explanation\n\nSearch Results:\n{{ JSON.stringify($json.results) }}",
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
