        "subject": "={{ 'Mobile App Development Proposal for ' + $json.school_name }}",
        "message": "=<html>\n<body style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;\">\n\n<h2 style=\"color: #2c3e50;\">Dear Principal / Admin,</h2>\n\n<p>Greetings from <strong>[Your Company Name]</strong>!</p>\n\n<p>I came across <strong>{{ $json.school_name }}</strong> in <strong>{{ $json.district }}</strong> and was truly impressed by your commitment to excellence in education, especially your IIT/NEET coaching programs.</p>\n\n<p>I noticed that your school does not yet have a <strong>dedicated mobile app</strong>. In today's digital world, a mobile app can significantly enhance your school's reach and parent engagement.</p>\n\n<h3 style=\"color: #27ae60;\">📱 What I Can Build For You:</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>✅ Student Portal (Results, Attendance, Timetable)</li>\n  <li>✅ Parent Communication App</li>\n  <li>✅ Online Fee Payment</li>\n  <li>✅ Push Notifications for Exams & Events</li>\n  <li>✅ IIT/NEET Study Materials & Videos</li>\n  <li>✅ Live Class Integration</li>\n  <li>✅ Admin Dashboard</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3 style=\"color: #e74c3c;\">🎯 Why Choose Us:</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>🏆 Built specifically for Telangana schools</li>\n  <li>💰 Affordable pricing plans</li>\n  <li>🔧 Free maintenance for 3 months</li>\n  <li>📱 Android + iOS both platforms</li>\n  <li>⚡ Ready in 30 days</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div style=\"background: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;\">\n  <h3 style=\"margin: 0; color: #2c3e50;\">🎁 Special Offer</h3>\n  <p style=\"margin: 10px 0 0 0;\">FREE DEMO for your school - No commitment required!</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>Please reply to this email or call us to schedule a <strong>FREE demonstration</strong>.</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-top: 30px;\">\n  <strong>Best Regards,</strong><br>\n  [Your Name]<br>\n  [Your Company]<br>\n  📞 [Your Phone Number]<br>\n  📧 [Your Email]<br>\n  🌐 [Your Website]\n</p>\n\n</body>\n</html>",
